<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.570119>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Scanning electron microscopy and bright field microscopy images of Thecacineta calix (Schröder, 1907) adhering to meiofaunal organisms: a) morpho-type I on Croconema cinctum; b) morpho-type II on Desmodorella tenuispiculum; c) morpho-type II on Desmodorella tenuispiculum; d) budding trophont on harpacticoid copepod." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/570119/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

